    "In addition, there are several studies adopting algorithms to handle the processing of an image or a video.",
    "An algorithm may, for instance, take into account individual video frames and attempt to locate instances of spatial inconsistency.",
    "Alternatively, the algorithm may compare successive video frames in an effort to identify instances of temporal inconsistency.In this research, we propose transfer learning of CNNs and hybrid CNN-Recurrent Neural Network (RNN) models with Particle Swarm Optimization (PSO)-based hyperparameter selection for deepfake detection.",
